{"tid":1723911,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"請CUSU宣布中大防衛戰勝利","createTime":"2019-11-15T10:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:00:59.000Z","uid":249705,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea0cae593740f751590e9d03b8aff13adf9384d","tid":1723911,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:19:35.000Z","msg":"首先多謝閪閪巴<br />\n<blockquote>宣佈中大防護戰勝利，停止分化，<br />\n召回中大人重整學園</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723451</a><br />\n<br />\n建議公開信包含以下幾項要點<br />\n1. 宣布中大防衛戰勝利<br />\n2. 感謝八方支援<br />\n3. 譴責政府今早封閉吐露港公路<br />\n4. 譴責警方非法攻擊學校行為<br />\n5. 重申五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解要宣佈防衛戰勝利?</span><br />\n<br />\n「凝聚士氣 打擊對方軍心」<br />\n1. 政府分化技倆失效<br />\n2. 曱甴怨政府唔俾攻<br />\n3. 藍絲屌警甴廢<br />\n4. 中大及支援手足整頓休息<br />\n5. 抗爭陣營重新調配人力物力<br />\n<br />\n另外建議星期六日全力支援黃店<br />\n下星期一至五繼續黎明行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你若退後 我城誰佑?</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6aJsDAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aJsDAo.jpg&h=3f28d1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhHANtK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhHANtK.jpg&h=77ad0da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NauRVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NauRVq.jpg&h=3c1fe6e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zH7hgm6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzH7hgm6.jpg&h=dd7b1436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DujO7tW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDujO7tW.jpg&h=55269ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYcw5fC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYcw5fC.jpg&h=681dd6bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"192bb2b7d965c8d2